OL,3,CHottest parts of UK revealed as
OL,4,Ctemperatures set to soar this week
OL,6,FIn another instance of meteorological
OL,7,Fwhiplash, temperatures are set to soar
OL,8,Facross the UK this week as the clear
OL,9,Fup from Storm Dave continues.
OL,11,FTake a look below to see how hot it
OL,12,Fwill get where you live.
OL,14,FWhy are the temperatures rising?
OL,16,FAs Storm Dave - which brought wind
OL,17,Fgusts of 93 mph - pulls away to the
OL,18,Feast, another deep area of low
OL,19,Fpressure builds in the Atlantic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
