OL,3,CHottest parts of UK revealed as
OL,4,Ctemperatures set to soar this week
OL,6,FThe position of this low is creating a
OL,7,Fsouth or southeasterly airflow across
OL,8,Fthe UK on Tuesday, tapping into the
OL,9,Fwarm, dry continental air.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FHow warm will it get this week?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
