OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775488261
OL,3,CHottest parts of UK revealed as
OL,4,Ctemperatures set to soar this week
OL,6,FTuesday will be the most widely warm
OL,7,Fand sunny day across the UK, with all
OL,8,Fareas seeing temperatures rise above
OL,9,Faverage - just a few degrees above
OL,10,Facross Northern Ireland and the west
OL,11,Fof Scotland, but up to 10 degrees
OL,12,Ffurther south.
OL,14,FWarmest areas are likely to be across
OL,15,Fthe south and West Midlands, Wales and
OL,16,Fnorth Devon, with highs likely
OL,17,Ftouching 22C there.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
