OL,3,CHottest parts of UK revealed as
OL,4,Ctemperatures set to soar this week
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, the temperatures will
OL,7,Flikely rise further in lighter winds,
OL,8,Fto around 24C, but the warmest areas
OL,9,Fwill tend to be restricted to east and
OL,10,Fsoutheastern England as the winds veer
OL,11,Fmore west or southwersterly.
OL,13,FStill plenty of sunshine to be had on
OL,14,FWednesday for much of the day.
OL,16,FHow unusual are these temperatures?
OL,17,FThey're not unusual at all - spring
OL,18,Fbrings huge temperature swings from
OL,19,Fovernight frosts to lovely warm days.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
