OL,3,CHottest parts of UK revealed as
OL,4,Ctemperatures set to soar this week
OL,6,FProbably only Tuesday and Wednesday as
OL,7,Fwind and rain is expected to move in
OL,8,Ffrom the west on Wednesday night
OL,9,Fbringing a return of the colder
OL,10,FAtlantic air and potentially snow
OL,11,Facross the Penines and Scottish
OL,12,FMountains.
OL,14,FSo plan for some lovely weather after
OL,15,Fsuch a wild weekend - the calm after
OL,16,Fthe storm wont last long!
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
